msgid "**Algorithm:**"
msgstr "**算法：**"

#: src/architecture/multi-agent.md
msgid "**Aliased workspace** — `<install>/agents/<alias>/workspace/`. One per agent. Holds the agent's identity files (`AGENTS.md`, `SOUL.md`, `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, `BOOTSTRAP.md`, `MEMORY.md`) and any operator data the agent owns."
msgstr "**别名工作区** — `<install>/agents/<alias>/workspace/`。每个 agent 一个。存放该 agent 的身份文件（`AGENTS.md`、`SOUL.md`、`IDENTITY.md`、`USER.md`、`BOOTSTRAP.md`、`MEMORY.md`）以及该 agent 拥有的所有操作员数据。"

