msgid "**Cron delivery:** `delivery.to` should be a plain room id (`!abc:server`) or alias (`#room:server`). Older configs that wrote `<sender>||<room>` are tolerated — ZeroClaw extracts the last `!`/`#`\\-prefixed segment and warns about the malformed value."
msgstr "**Cron 投递：** `delivery.to` 应为普通房间 id（`!abc:server`）或别名（`#room:server`）。对于写成 `<sender>||<room>` 的旧配置仍可兼容——ZeroClaw 会提取最后一个以 `!`/`#` 开头的片段，并对格式错误的值发出警告。"

