msgstr "**去重** — 防止重复处理同一条消息（重启、重试）"

#: src/tools/mcp.md
msgid "**Deferred Loading**: Keeping `deferred_loading = true` reduces the initial token overhead by only sending tool names to the LLM. The agent will fetch the full schema only when it decides to use the tool."
msgstr "**延迟加载**：将 `deferred_loading = true` 设置为启用状态，可以通过仅向 LLM 发送工具名称来减少初始令牌开销。智能体将在决定使用工具时再获取完整的模式。"

