#: src/foundations/fnd-005-contribution-culture.md
msgid "**Explain the principle, not just the verdict.** If you ask someone to change something, tell them why. \"Change X to Y\" produces a fix. \"Change X to Y because Z\" produces understanding that applies to the next ten situations where the same principle applies."
