#: src/architecture/subagents.md
msgid "**From cron**: `JobType::Agent` jobs run through `run_agent_job` (`crates/zeroclaw-runtime/src/cron/scheduler.rs:339`) which builds the same `SubAgentContext` but flags the child as a top-level run (not a SubAgent) so it can itself spawn one level of subagent."
msgstr "**来自 cron**：`JobType::Agent` 任务通过 `run_agent_job`（`crates/zeroclaw-runtime/src/cron/scheduler.rs:339`）运行，它会构建相同的 `SubAgentContext`，但将子任务标记为顶层运行（而非 SubAgent），以便它自身可以再生成一层 subagent。"

