msgid "**Inline diff comments** for every 🔴 blocking, 🟡 warning, or 🔵 suggestion finding tied to a specific line. Anchor the feedback to the code so the author can resolve it inline."
msgstr "**内联差异评论**用于标记每一处与特定行相关的 🔴 阻断、🟡 警告或 🔵 建议类问题。将反馈锚定到代码，便于作者就地解决。"

