msgid "Doc translations live in `docs/book/po/`. `cargo mdbook sync` runs extract → merge → strip obsolete → AI-fill in one step. Without `--model-provider`, sync still runs extract + merge and reports how many strings need translation — partial translations fall back to English at render time."
msgstr "文档翻译位于 `docs/book/po/`。`cargo mdbook sync` 一步完成 extract → merge → strip obsolete → AI-fill 流程。如果不指定 `--model-provider`，sync 仍会运行 extract + merge 并报告需要翻译的字符串数量——未翻译的部分会在渲染时回退为英文。"

