msgid "Every model provider lives at `[providers.models.<type>.<alias>]` in `~/.zeroclaw/config.toml`. `<type>` is the canonical family slot (`anthropic`, `openai`, `azure`, `gemini`, `groq`, `moonshot`, ...). `<alias>` is your operator-assigned instance name — pick any descriptive name (`home`, `work`, `cn`, `gpt5`, ...)."
msgstr "每个模型提供方都位于 `~/.zeroclaw/config.toml` 中的 `[providers.models.<type>.<alias>]`。`<type>` 是规范的家族槽位（`anthropic`、`openai`、`azure`、`gemini`、`groq`、`moonshot`……）。`<alias>` 是你为实例指定的运维名称——可任选一个具有描述性的名称（`home`、`work`、`cn`、`gpt5`……）。"

