#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md
msgid "Technology changes. It changes faster with each iteration than it did the time before, and that rate is accelerating. The specific tools in this document — Rust, `cargo`, `clippy`, the OpenTelemetry SDK, the AI assistants the team uses today — will be superseded. Some of them within the lifetime of this project. The platforms will change. The languages will evolve. The tooling ecosystem will look different in five years than it does today, and different again in ten."
