#: src/contributing/architecture-map.md
msgid "This map does not replace the [RFC process](./rfcs.md) or the PR template. It exists to make architecture and contribution scope easier to find. After RFC #6808 policy slices are promoted, follow [FND-003](../foundations/fnd-003-governance.md), [Labels](../maintainers/labels.md), [PR workflow](../maintainers/pr-workflow.md), and [Reviewer playbook](../maintainers/reviewer-playbook.md)."
