#: src/gateway/api.md
msgid "`PATCH /api/config` accepts a JSON Patch document (RFC 6902). The supported op subset is `add`, `replace`, `remove`, `test`. Each op runs against an in-memory copy of the config; once every op has applied, `Config::validate()` runs once on the result. If validation passes, the new state is persisted and swapped in. If any op or the final validation fails, on-disk and in-memory state are unchanged."
msgstr "`PATCH /api/config` 接受 JSON Patch 文档（RFC 6902）。支持的 op 子集为 `add`、`replace`、`remove`、`test`。每个 op 都针对配置的内存副本执行；当所有 op 都已应用后，`Config::validate()` 会对结果执行一次。如果验证通过，新状态将被持久化并切换生效。如果任何 op 或最终验证失败，磁盘上和内存中的状态都将保持不变。"

