msgid "`external_peers` lists humans or external bots the group expects on the same channel; the runtime accepts inbound from those usernames as cross-agent traffic. `ignore` is a per-group blocklist that subtracts from the resolved peer set every member sees — useful for excluding a specific bot account that's noisy."
